<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Admin Notification - KoreaBiz Directory</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h1 style="color: #dc3545;">Admin Notification</h1>
    
    <h2 style="color: #333;">{{subject}}</h2>
    
    <p><strong>Timestamp:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
    
    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <h3>Details:</h3>
        <pre style="white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px;">{{data}}</pre>
    </div>
    
    <p>Please review this notification and take appropriate action if required.</p>
    
    <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 12px;">
        This is an automated notification from KoreaBiz Directory Admin System.
    </p>
</body>
</html>